com.zendesk.sdk.network.impl

Class ZendeskCallback<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.zendesk.sdk.network.impl.ZendeskCallback<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of object that will be returned upon a successful API call

    public abstract class ZendeskCallback<T>
extends Object
    This abstract class is used to define success and error callbacks that are used in API calls. It is used so that we do not rely on a specific callback implementation of the http library that we use.
